                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>&lt;b>You are encouraged to report negative side effects of prescription drugs to the FDA. Visit www.fda.gov/medwatch, or call 1-800-FDA-1088 (1-800-332-1088).&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Medical Information Requests:&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;If you are a healthcare professional&amp;nbsp;or a patient or caregiver&amp;nbsp;and would like to search for product information or submit an inquiry to the AbbVie&amp;nbsp;Medical&amp;nbsp;Information team, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbviemedinfo.com/&quot; title=&quot;https://www.abbviemedinfo.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>www.abbviemedinfo.com&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
